  "title": "第一家法律 AI 公司，死于不够 AI",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNTY1MjE2OA==&mid=2247492126&idx=1&sn=3da8c177a84f08fd20d17852156fe693",
  "date": "2025-11-28 11:01:00",
  "author": "乌鸦智能说",
